    {
      "block_id": "doxlgPPZen07DE71krz6lnZU97b",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "最近 AI 圈最火的话题，莫过于 OpenClaw（小龙虾）了。这个项目从诞生到现在改了三次名字，热度却一路飙升。很多人都在问：它和 Claude Code 有什么区别？为什么说它是“主动式 AI Agent”？普通人能不能用起来？",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgttB8rwrd3BTYes2rRTUOde",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "2 月 24 日晚上，WaytoAGI 社区邀请了 00 后开发者来新璐，带大家深入拆解了 OpenClaw 的技术架构。这场直播信息量巨大，我把核心内容整理成这篇文章，让你彻底搞懂小龙虾到底是怎么回事。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlggIrm799oUpFpWhohvOC5od",
      "block_type": 4,
      "block_type_name": "heading2",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "从 Claude Code 到 OpenClaw:AI Agent 的进化史",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgwM8lT4toOw0Ps2Urpx55Ic",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "要理解 OpenClaw，得先回顾一下 AI Agent 的发展脉络。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgZ6Cy67xbputM8Q3xwnuFpe",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "去年 2 月，Anthropic 发布了 Claude Code，让 AI 能够通过命令行帮你写代码、改文件。到了 5 月，国内开发者开始大规模使用。11 月前后，连非程序员都开始用 Claude Code 完成各种任务。这期间，Cursor、OpenCode 等工具也陆续出现。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlg1ok9prGIIdVs74obo5oUgf",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "但这些工具有个共同特点：被动。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgu7cBPd7kW3eJK3kcYFIwDg",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "什么意思？就像你用 Claude Code 时，必须打开一个终端窗口，给它发任务，它才会干活。任务完成后，你通常会关掉这个会话，下次再开一个新的。为什么？因为上下文会“污染”——聊得越多，AI 越容易跑偏，所以很多程序员习惯频繁清空对话，保持干净的工作环境。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgqRdNxJkk8VNHAMv2PhgUph",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "这就是被动式、临时性 Agent 的典型特征：你踹它一脚，它动一下。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgeEUDyJiE53yMX2suyOFBrc",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "OpenClaw 的革命性在于：它是主动式 Agent。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlg4Ct2GDVS4DbTkbBp79aRgh",
      "block_type": 4,
      "block_type_name": "heading2",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "OpenClaw 的两大核心机制",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgYBIbmbbsT9bGvllN2I9pze",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "OpenClaw 的 Agent 核心其实用的是 Py Agent 框架，这个框架本质上是 Claude Code 的最小化实现——只用 143 行代码，就实现了 bash、read、write、edit 这几个基础工具。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgegswSt1MXT5jjWw0WCj9nd",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "那它凭什么变得“主动”？答案是两个关键机制：Cron 定时任务和 Heartbeat 心跳。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgGWBTHvTwF0BXgssKXglHSc",
      "block_type": 5,
      "block_type_name": "heading3",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "机制一：Cron 定时任务——让 AI 学会“记事”",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgsEwmN64mSvKUR3YSWYPskg",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "Cron 是 Linux 系统里的定时任务工具。OpenClaw 把这个机制引入了 AI Agent，让它能够：",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgOygUQKan0MujF7H7Ui9Gkg",
      "block_type": 13,
      "block_type_name": "ordered",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "一次性任务（Once）：比如你说“明天下午 3 点提醒我开会”，它会在指定时间执行一次，然后自动删除这个任务。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgUVrymkJ1gHOBh3yCU4zuWf",
      "block_type": 13,
      "block_type_name": "ordered",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "周期性任务（Every）：比如“每天早上 10 点给我一个惊喜”，它会根据你的聊天记录和兴趣，每天定时推送内容。可能是你关注的技术动态，可能是黄金价格走势，也可能是某个开源项目的最新 issue。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlg1rwC0OmAQ5yokKuyd2bhDg",
      "block_type": 13,
      "block_type_name": "ordered",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "Cron 表达式任务：更灵活的定时规则，比如“每周一到周五早上 9 点”。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
